            . I am master of the Infant-school, <placeName id="t18310908-335-crimeloc1725">Baldwin's-gardens</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18310908-335-crimeloc1725" type="placeName" value="Baldwin's-gardens"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18310908-335-crimeloc1725" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310908-335-off1723 t18310908-335-crimeloc1725"></join>. On the 13th of August I saw the prisoner coming from Mr. Marsh's house opposite, with something under his apron; I informed Mr. Marsh, who I had seen go into a neighbour's house a minute before.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18310908-335-person2419">
                  WILLIAM 
                  MARSH
               <interp inst="t18310908-335-person2419" type="surname" value="MARSH"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310908-335-person2419" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310908-335-person2419" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I keep a shoemaker's shop, in Baldwin's-gardens. Eastford gave me information; I saw the prisoner about twenty yards off - he dropped something, and when I came up he said, "There are your shoes, I hope you will not prosecute me;" I took them up, and took him to the office.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18310908-335-person2420">
                  ANDREW 
                  LLOYD
               <interp inst="t18310908-335-person2420" type="surname" value="LLOYD"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310908-335-person2420" type="given" value="ANDREW"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310908-335-person2420" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I asked the prisoner why he took the shoes; he said it was wholly through distress.</p>
               <p>The prisoner received a good character.</p>
